body.paragraph:
Āpattādhikaraṇaṃ āpattānāpattīti? Āpattādhikaraṇaṃ āpatti. Kiṃ pana āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā āpattiṃ āpajjeyyāti? Āma, āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā āpattiṃ āpajjeyya. Āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā kati āpattiyo āpajjati? Āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā catasso āpattiyo āpajjati. Bhikkhunī jānaṃ pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ 
Note { id=1, line='6', referenceLine='31', original='pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ ajjhāpannaṃ (syā.)', type='auto', previous=' āpattiyo āpajjati. Bhikkhunī jānaṃ pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='syā.', text='pārājikaṃ dhammaṃ ajjhāpannaṃ'}}
paṭicchādeti, āpatti pārājikassa; vematikā paṭicchādeti, āpatti thullaccayassa; bhikkhu saṅghādisesaṃ paṭicchādeti, āpatti pācittiyassa; ācāravipattiṃ paṭicchādeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa – āpattādhikaraṇapaccayā imā catasso āpattiyo āpajjati.

Tattha katamaṃ kiccaṃ no adhikaraṇaṃ? Ācariyakiccaṃ upajjhāyakiccaṃ 
Note { id=7, line='30', referenceLine='76', original='upajjhāyakiccaṃ sakiccaṃ (ka.)', type='auto', previous='Tattha katamaṃ kiccaṃ no adhikaraṇaṃ? Ācariyakiccaṃ upajjhāyakiccaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='Ācariyakiccaṃ upajjhāyakiccaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='upajjhāyakiccaṃ sakiccaṃ'}}
samānupajjhāyakiccaṃ samānācariyakiccaṃ – idaṃ kiccaṃ no adhikaraṇaṃ.
